  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀλεξάνδρο\n                    υ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀλεξάνδρο\n                    υ\">Ἀλεξάνδρο-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>υ</span></span> κὲ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ῥοδόπης\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ῥοδόπης\">Ῥοδόπης</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>μνημίων ἐνγ-<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ὺς ἐπισκόπου ὁ <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Χεπερίωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Χεπερίωνος\">Χεπερίωνος</span></span> ὃ ἐ-<br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>πώλησεν <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἑρμιό\n                    νη ἡ θυγάτηρ Κε\n                    σαρίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἑρμιό\n                    νη\">Ἑρμιό-<br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>νη</span> ἡ θυγάτηρ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κε\n                    σαρίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κε\n                    σαρίου\">Κε-<br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>σαρίου</span></span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀλεξάνδρο\n                    υ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀλεξάνδρο\n                    υ\">ΑΛΕΞΑΝΔΡΟ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>Υ</span></span>ΚΕ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ῥοδόπης\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ῥοδόπης\">ΡΟΔΟΠΗΣ</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΜΝΗΜΙΩΝΕΝΓ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΥΣΕΠΙΣΚΟΠΟΥΟ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Χεπερίωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Χεπερίωνος\">ΧΕΠΕΡΙΩΝΟΣ</span></span>ΟΕ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ΠΩΛΗΣΕΝ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἑρμιό\n                    νη ἡ θυγάτηρ Κε\n                    σαρίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἑρμιό\n                    νη\">ΕΡΜΙΟ<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ΝΗ</span>ΗΘΥΓΑΤΗΡ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κε\n                    σαρίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κε\n                    σαρίου\">ΚΕ<br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>ΣΑΡΙΟΥ</span></span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001520_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001520_tiled-thumb.tif